---
title: Pan-Fried Sea Bream with Sticky Asian Sauce, Herby Rice and Charred Bok Choy
description: We love a good Bream with Rice and Bok Choy and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pan-fried-bream-c12e923d-b4e7cf23.jpg
